Ebbro 44767 Nissan Skyline GT-R 1995 SUGO GT Championship (JGTC Round 5) M. Kageyama/K. Hoshino 2nd Place

Masahiko Kageyama & Kazuyoshi Hoshino drove this Skyline in round 5 of the 1995 JGTC Series - SUGO GT Championship. They qualified in 2nd place and finished the race in 2nd place.
